description: Brock the jock and power bottom Lane enjoy a day in the surf, hanging out by the pier. Lane’s is excited to “crush another Sean Cody film,” well actually he’s excited for Brock to crush it. Lane claims he’s “just going to be sitting there, but Brock laughs and says Lane’s “going to be doing some work too.” If you want to know exactly what they’ll get up to you’ll just have to “stay tuned and find out,” says Brock.
title: Brock & Lane: Bareback
